<main>

  <div class="card card-image" style="background-image: url(https://tocacares.s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/feet-around-ball.jpg);background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover;">
    <div class="text-white text-center rgba-black-strong py-5 px-4">
      <div>
        <%= image_tag "TOCA_CARES_LOGO_FNL7.png", class: "pt-5 mb-5" %>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
          <div class="container">
            <p class="h5 text-left thin mb-3">
              The employees and shareholders of TOCA have established this fund to:
              <ul class="text-left h5 thin">
                <li class="mb-1"><strong>Support</strong> each other in times of financial stress</li>
                <li class="mb-1">Encourage each other to further our <strong>education</strong></li>
                <li>Reach out to our local community through involvement with and giving to <strong>charity</strong></li>
              </ul>
            </p>
            <div class="thin-white-box my-5 px-5 py-3">
              <p class="h5">
                By participating in this program, you have made a commitment to strengthen and value your&nbsp;teammates.
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class="h5 thin mb-5">
              Explore how this works and feel the love.
            </p>
          </div> <!-- container -->
        </div> <!-- row -->
        <%= link_to page_path(:apply), class: "btn btn-secondary btn-lg" do %>Apply Now<% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="container mt-5 px-3 text-center">
    <h2>
      The strength of the team is each member. <br class="d-none d-md-block">The strength of each member is&nbsp;the&nbsp;team.
      <br><em><small>―Phil Jackson</small></em>
    </h2>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
     <section class="text-center">
       <div class="row mt-5 mb-3 wow fadeIn">

           <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
               <div class="card">
                   <div class="view overlay"> <!-- image -->
                       <%= image_tag "hardship.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Young man trying to fix a broken down car." %>
                       <a href="https://mdbootstrap.com/education/tech-marketing/automated-app-introduction/" target="_blank">
                           <div class="mask rgba-white-slight"></div></a>
                   </div>
                   <div class="card-body h-100">
                       <!--Title-->
                       <h4 class="card-title toca-uppercase">Hardship</h4>
                       <h5 class="card-quote color-toca-red">
                         When the going gets tough – the tough get going!
                         <br><em><small>―John Belushi</small></em>
                       </h5>
                       <p class="card-text">
                         78% of U.S. workers are living paycheck to paycheck. Unexpected financial challenges can cause good people to go tilt.
                         <br><br>
                         TOCACares wants to provide a limited but immediate financial safety net when you face an auto repair, health care, or other unexpected challenge that you cannot afford to meet.
                       </p>
                       <%= link_to new_hardship_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" do %>
                          Apply Now
                       <% end %>
                  </div>
               </div> <!-- card -->
           </div> <!--Grid column-->

           <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
             <div class="card">
               <div class="view overlay"> <!-- image -->
                 <%= image_tag "scholarship.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Woman graduating from college." %>
                 <a href="https://mdbootstrap.com/education/tech-marketing/automated-app-introduction/" target="_blank">
                   <div class="mask rgba-white-slight"></div>
                 </a>
               </div>
               <div class="card-body h-100">
                 <!--Title-->
                 <h4 class="card-title toca-uppercase">Scholarship</h4>
                 <!--Text-->
                 <h5 class="card-quote color-toca-red">
                   Knowledge is a weapon. I intend to be formidably armed.
                   <br><em><small>―Terry Goodkind</small></em>
                 </h5>
                 <p class="card-text">
                   We can always grow and improve.  TOCA Cares will pay up to 80% of the cost of classes (including college) up to a maximum contribution per year based upon your years of service to the company.
                   <br><br>
                   Whether this is a class learning to code, cook, or completing your degree, TOCA Cares wants to support you expanding your mind and honing your skills.
                 </p>
                 <%= link_to new_scholarship_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" do %>
                 Apply Now
                 <% end %>
               </div>
             </div> <!-- card -->
           </div> <!--Grid column-->
           <!--Grid column-->

           <!--Grid column-->
           <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
               <div class="card">
                   <div class="view overlay"> <!-- image -->
                       <%= image_tag "charity.jpg", class: "card-img-top", alt: "Young man building a house for charity." %>
                       <a href="https://mdbootstrap.com/education/tech-marketing/automated-app-introduction/" target="_blank">
                           <div class="mask rgba-white-slight"></div>
                       </a>
                   </div>
                   <div class="card-body">
                       <!--Title-->
                       <h4 class="card-title toca-uppercase">Charity</h4>
                       <h5 class="card-quote color-toca-red">
                         Service to others is the rent you pay for your room here on earth.
                         <br><em><small>―Mohammed Ali</small></em>
                       </h5>
                       <p class="card-text">
                         Our team is going to positively impact each community we touch.  TOCACares wants to support your involvement in local charities.
                         <br><br>
                         If you have an idea of how to work with registered charities, TOCACares will pay 80% of your costs or in some case make direct contributions.
                       </p>
                       <%= link_to new_charity_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" do %>
                        Apply Now
                       <% end %>
                   </div>
               </div> <!-- card -->
           </div> <!--Grid column-->

      </div> <!-- row -->
    </section>

   </div> <!-- container -->
 </main>




<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function() {
     $('.card-img-top').matchHeight();
     $('.card-quote').matchHeight();
     $('.card-text').matchHeight();
   });
</script>
